{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-quiz-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/quiz-javascript-objects/quiz-javascript-objects","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Pokušao sam sa malim deo kodova za JavaScript","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da biste položili kratki test, morate tačno odgovoriti na najmanje 18 od 20 pitanja koja su navedena ispod.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":8,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","superBlock":"introduction-to-objects-in-javascript","block":"quiz-javascript-objects","fields":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/#quiz-javascript-objects","slug":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/quiz-javascript-objects/quiz-javascript-objects"},"quizzes":[{"questions":[{"distractors":["<p>Kolekcija parova ključ-vrednost.</p>","<p>Kontejner sa karakteristikama i putevima.</p>","<p>Neprimitivni tip podataka (non-primitive).</p>"],"text":"<p>Ili je među sljedećim što ne opisuje objekt u JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p>Osnovni tip podataka (primitivan).</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>const book = { \"pages\": 255 };</code></p>","<p><code>const car = { year: 2025 };</code></p>","<p><code>const person = { \"name\": \"nora\" };</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koje od sledećih definicija/objašnjenja nije važeće?</p>","answer":"<p><code>const product = { color: blue };</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>person -> job</code></p>","<p><code>person#job</code></p>","<p><code>person[job]</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Kako se može dobiti svojstvo <code>job</code> za ovaj objekat od <code>person</code>?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let person = { job: \"Software Developer\" };\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>person.job</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>person -> address -> street</code></p>","<p><code>person#address#street</code></p>","<p><code>person[address.street]</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Da li možete dobiti karakteristiku <code>street</code> za predmet <code>person</code> koji je dole?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const person = {\n  address: {\n    street: \"sample-street\"\n  }\n};\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>person[\"address\"][\"street\"]</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Ključ atributa koji je poznat i nepromenljiv.</p>","<p>Ključ atributa koji je ugnježdjen kroz više nivoa objekta.</p>","<p>Ključ karakteristike koja možda ne postoji u nečemu.</p>"],"text":"<p>Koje kriterijume među ovim se mogu pronaći samo korišćenjem notacije u uglastim zagradama?</p>","answer":"<p>Dinamički ključ atributa.</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>const name = person.name;</code></p>","<p><code>const name = person[\"name\"];</code></p>","<p><code>const { ...name } = person;</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja od sljedećih koristi dekonstrukciju (destructuring) da bi tačno dobila svojstvo <code>name</code> objekta <code>person</code> prikazanog ispod?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const person = { name: \"John\" }\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>const { name } = person;</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>const flour = recipe.ingredients.flour;</code></p>","<p><code>const flour = recipe[\"ingredients\"][\"flour\"];</code></p>","<p><code>const { ingredients: flour } = recipe;</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koji od sljedećih koristi destrukturiranje (destructuring) kako bi ispravno dobio svojstvo <code>flour</code> objekta <code>recipe</code> ispod?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const recipe = {\n  ingredients: {\n    flour: \"2 cups\",\n    sugar: \"1 cup\"\n  }\n};\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>const { ingredients: { flour } } = recipe;</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>const key = object.key &#x26;&#x26; \"defaultValue\";</code></p>","<p><code>const key = object.key || \"defaultValue\";</code></p>","<p><code>const { key: \"defaultValue\" } = object;</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Da li je moguće postaviti podrazumevanu vrednost za ključ svojstva kada koristite rešenje dizajna u JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p><code>const { key = \"defaultValue\" } = object;</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>year.hasProperty(\"car\");</code></p>","<p><code>car.hasProperty(\"year\");</code></p>","<p><code>car.hasOwnProperty(year);</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Da li možete proveriti da li objekat sa <code>car</code> ima svojstvo od <code>year</code>?</p>","answer":"<p><code>car.hasOwnProperty(\"year\");</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Niz slova povezan sa nečim.</p>","<p>Red podataka povezan sa objektom.</p>","<p>Broj povezan sa predmetom.</p>"],"text":"<p>Koja je putanja za nešto?</p>","answer":"<p>Funkcija povezana sa objektom.</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>calculator#add(10, 7);</code></p>","<p><code>calculator.call(add(10, 7));</code></p>","<p><code>add.calculator(10, 7);</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Kako mogu pozvati metodu <code>add</code> ovog objekta <code>calculator</code> da doda brojeve <code>10</code> i <code>7</code>?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const calculator = {\n  add: function(a, b) {\n    return a + b;\n  }\n};\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>calculator.add(10, 7);</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>remove</code></p>","<p><code>erase</code></p>","<p><code>discard</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koji stručnjak skida karakteristike sa nečega?</p>","answer":"<p><code>delete</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>player in \"score\"</code></p>","<p><code>player in score</code></p>","<p><code>score in player</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Da li možete proveriti da li atribut <code>score</code> postoji u objektu <code>player</code>?</p>","answer":"<p><code>\"score\" in player</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>object() new</code></p>","<p><code>new object()</code></p>","<p><code>Object() new</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Kako možete kreirati nešto potpuno novo u JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p><code>new Object()</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>object?key</code></p>","<p><code>object.[\"key\"]</code></p>","<p><code>object.?key</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja sintaksa je tačna pri korišćenju sekvencijalnog povezivanja (optional chaining) u JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p><code>object?.key</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p>Koristi se za definisanje parametara sa podrazumevanim vrednostima.</p>","<p>Koristi se za definisanje opcionih putanja unutar objekta koje možda mogu biti pozvane ili ne.</p>","<p>Koristi se za pisanje kratkog koda za spajanje više poziva metoda u jedan izraz.</p>"],"text":"<p>Zašto se serijska konekcija koristi u JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p>Koristi se za sigurno dobijanje svojstava objekta koji mogu biti <code>null</code> ili <code>undefined</code>.</p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>Stringify.toJSON()</code></p>","<p><code>JSON.toObject()</code></p>","<p><code>Object.toJSON()</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja se putanja koristi za konverziju stvari JavaScript u niz znakova JSON?</p>","answer":"<p><code>JSON.stringify()</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>JSON.toObject()</code></p>","<p><code>JSON.convert()</code></p>","<p><code>JSON.object()</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koja putanja menja niz slova JSON nazad u nešto kao JavaScript?</p>","answer":"<p><code>JSON.parse()</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>toy.color</code></p>","<p><code>toy[color]</code></p>","<p><code>color[toy]</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Koji od ovih ima svojstvo <code>color</code> objekta <code>toy</code> korišćenjem uglastih zagrada?</p>","answer":"<p><code>toy[\"color\"]</code></p>","audioData":null},{"distractors":["<p><code>learner.name.phone.home</code></p>","<p><code>learner.email.work</code></p>","<p><code>learner.contact.home</code></p>"],"text":"<p>Kako da dobijem broj <code>home</code> ovog predmeta <code>learner</code> u JavaScript koristeći dot notaciju?</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const learner = {\n  name: \"Nora\",\n  age: 45,\n  contact: {\n    email: \"nora@email.com\",\n    phone: {\n      home: \"123-456-7890\",\n      work: \"098-765-4321\"\n    }\n  }\n};\n</code></pre>","answer":"<p><code>learner.contact.phone.home</code></p>","audioData":null}]}],"tests":[],"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/#quiz-javascript-objects","dashedName":"quiz-javascript-objects","certification":"introduction-to-objects-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-to-objects-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"quiz-javascript-objects","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lecture-working-with-loops/how-do-loops-and-iteration-work-in-javascript","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/review-javascript-objects/review-javascript-objects","id":"66edcd0ecb4b25dc64a34804","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":8,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-to-objects-in-javascript/quiz-javascript-objects/quiz-javascript-objects"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}